## Summary
This documentation details the integration between Amplitude Data and Amazon Kinesis Data Stream, explaining how to set up event streaming from Amplitude to Kinesis by creating an AWS IAM role with specific permissions, configuring a Kinesis stream, and establishing the connection in Amplitude's destination catalog.

